title: DPRK Red Star OS 2.0
description: Seeded by kekd Please refer to the Readme.txt included. ---------------------------------------------------------- Red Star Linux Operating System: Like to live dangerously? Why not download and run North Korea’s homebrew Linux distribution on your main computer? This distro is split into two .ISO files, and I am assuming you know what to do with them if you’re endeavoring to download them. The first disc is bootable, and allows you to install the North Korean OS, whereas the second disc is supplementary software. ---------------------------------------------------------- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_Star_OS
